# Precision: Requires 2+ signals within 60 minutes

## EQL Sequence Query

```eql
sequence by user.email with maxspan=60m
  [authentication where event.outcome == "success" and 
   not (source.ip in user_baseline.known_ips and 
        host.id in user_baseline.known_devices)]
  [file where event.action in ("download", "access", "share") and
   file.operation_count > user_baseline.threshold]
```

